  "instructions": [
    "Preheat grill to medium-high heat (400°F/200°C).",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together olive oil, lemon juice, garlic, paprika, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Place the skewers in a shallow dish and brush with marinade, making sure to coat evenly.",
    "Let the skewers marinate for at least 30 minutes, or up to 2 hours in the refrigerator.",
    "Grill the skewers for 8-10 minutes per side, or until they reach an internal temperature of 165°F (74°C).",
    "Let the skewers rest for 5 minutes before serving.",
    "Garnish with chopped cilantro and serve immediately."
